timelineManager.controller

Class AddTimelineController

  • java.lang.Object
    • timelineManager.controller.AbstractController
      • timelineManager.controller.AddTimelineController

  • public class AddTimelineController
extends AbstractController
    This is a controller class for the AddTimelineView. it holds the variables and logics needed to create a new timeline from GUI.
